00:49:24.256 --> 00:49:26.341
Bob! What have you...

744
00:49:29.261 --> 00:49:30.721
Stinks.

745
00:49:38.478 --> 00:49:39.646
Thank you.

746
00:49:45.277 --> 00:49:47.613
