753
00:50:03.795 --> 00:50:05.964
<i>...so that we can resolve
where the cat should be.</i>

754
00:50:14.264 --> 00:50:16.850
<i>And they say there's
a cold front coming in this weekend</i>

755
00:50:16.892 --> 00:50:18.227
