756
00:50:18.268 --> 00:50:20.395
- <i>Might even get a bit of snow.</i>
- Brilliant.

757
00:50:20.437 --> 00:50:23.524
<i>Could be a white Christmas this year.
How do we feel about that?</i>

758
00:50:23.565 --> 00:50:25.526
